,"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/Float/Model/Format/Basic.lean#L26-L36"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">structure</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Format/Basic.html#Float.Model.Format\"><span class=\"name\">Float</span>.<span class=\"name\">Model</span>.<span class=\"name\">Format</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A floating point format is specified by two pieces of information: the number\nof bits in the mantissa, and the number of bits in the exponent.\n","docLink":"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Format/Basic.html#Float.Model.Format","kind":"structure","line":26,"name":"Float.Model.Format","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/Float/Model/Format/Basic.lean#L26-L36"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Format/Basic.html#Float.Model.totalExponent\"><span class=\"name\">Float</span>.<span class=\"name\">Model</span>.<span class=\"name\">totalExponent</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">mantissa</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">exponent</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/Int/Basic.html#Int\">Int</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/Int/Basic.html#Int\">Int</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The position of the most significant digit, where the unit digit corresponds to `1`.\nSo, for example, `1.0b` has total exponent `1`, `0.1b` has total exponent `0`,\n`0.01b` has total exponent `-1`, and so on.\n","docLink":"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Format/Basic.html#Float.Model.totalExponent","kind":"def","line":18,"name":"Float.Model.totalExponent","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/Float/Model/Format/Basic.lean#L18-L24"}}],"imports":["Init.Data.Int.Basic","Init.Data.Nat.Log2"],"instances":[],"name":"Init.Data.Float.Model.Format.Basic"}